Treasure Hunting A Sunken Yacht | After The Storm | Action Crime Thriller | Full Movie

On the run from ruthless smugglers and the police; Arno (Bejamin Bratt); a world-weary scavenger; is hired as a courier for a rich tycoon. When the tycoon's luxury yacht goes down in a violent storm. Arno is forced to partner with a local crook (Armand Assante) and the race is on to salvage the bounty. Forming an uneasy alliance of mutual distrust; the reluctant partners grow increasingly wary which causes them to commit the ultimate betrayal.

2001. Stars: Benjamin Bratt, Mili Avital, Barbara Andres
